<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Debate Details</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: #f9fafb;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .hero {
      background-image: url('debate_image.jpg'); /* Replace with your debate image */
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      height: 250px;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-shadow: 1px 1px 5px black;
    }
    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    .tab-container {
      display: flex;
      margin: 20px;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #ccc;
    }

    .tab {
      padding: 10px 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #555;
      border-bottom: 3px solid transparent;
    }

    .tab.active {
      border-bottom: 3px solid #6366f1;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .tab-content {
      padding: 20px;
      display: none;
    }

    .tab-content.active {
      display: block;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hero" style="background-image: url('<%= debateImage %>');">
    <h1>Motion: This House Would Ban Autonomous Weapon Systems</h1>
</div>

  <div class="tab-container">
    <div class="tab active" onclick="switchTab('summary')">Team Summaries</div>
    <div class="tab" onclick="switchTab('oa')">Chair's Oral Adjudication</div>
  </div>

  <div id="summary" class="tab-content active">
    <h3>Opening Government</h3>
    <p>Outlined the humanitarian risks posed by autonomous weapons and emphasized accountability gaps.</p>

    <h3>Opening Opposition</h3>
    <p>Argued that such weapons reduce human casualties and increase strategic precision.</p>

    <h3>Closing Government</h3>
    <p>Added philosophical depth on moral agency, reinforcing why bans are ethically necessary.</p>

    <h3>Closing Opposition</h3>
    <p>Questioned enforceability of bans and emphasized geopolitical balance.</p>
  </div>

  <div id="oa" class="tab-content">
    <h3>Chair's Oral Adjudication</h3>
    <p>
      The win goes to Closing Government for bringing in unique analysis about accountability and
      ethics that substantially shifted the debate. Closing Opposition was strong but slightly repetitive.
    </p>
  </div>

  <script>
    function switchTab(tabId) {
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab').forEach(t => t.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelectorAll('.tab-content').forEach(c => c.classList.remove('active'));
      document.querySelector(`.tab[onclick="switchTab('${tabId}')"]`).classList.add('active');
      document.getElementById(tabId).classList.add('active');
    }
  </script>

</body>
</html>
